Tonight?

64
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:23,540
I probably can't go out tonight.

65
00:03:24,580 --> 00:03:25,930
Why? What's up?

66
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,370
Wanted to take a walk with you.

67
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:31,380
A walk?

68
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,920
Just us two?

69
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:37,830
Then... I'll try to go out.

70
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:39,580
Okay.

71
00:03:56,330 --> 00:03:57,170
Chen Jing'an.

72
00:04:00,410 --> 00:04:01,250
Chen Jing'an.

73
00:04:02,490 --> 00:04:03,760
There's something

74
00:04:04,410 --> 00:04:05,870
I've kept to myself for three years.

75
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:09,060
When you read this letter,

76
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,090
I want to tell you...

77
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:14,460
Tian Ye,

78
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:16,580
