82
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,990
Almost done!

83
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,020
Coming out now.

84
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:34,740
You're already in grade 11

85
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:36,410
and you haven't improved a bit.

86
00:04:36,490 --> 00:04:37,620
Only your toilet time

87
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:38,790
keeps increasing.

88
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,720
Move aside.

89
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:41,580
Move.

90
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:00,790
Tian Ye.

91
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:05,920
This kid...

92
00:05:06,410 --> 00:05:08,200
What's he up to all day?

93
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:21,420
What are you doing?

94
00:05:22,330 --> 00:05:23,170
Mom.

95
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,490
I brought you foot-soaking water.

96
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:26,870
You silly boy,

97
00:05:26,910 --> 00:05:27,910
it's not nighttime yet.

98
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:29,160
Why would I soak my feet now?

99
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,880
Mom,

100
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:32,910
you always say I never improve,

101
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,990
that I'm forever a child.

102
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:37,040
I'm almost in college.

103
00:05:37,410 --> 00:05:38,620
Shouldn't I show some growth?

104
00:05:46,910 --> 00:05:48,740
Why are you acting so strangely today?

105
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:51,160
Did you get into trouble?

106
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:53,620
Why do you always assume the worst?

107
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,000
Can't I just...

108
00:05:55,410 --> 00:05:56,250
suddenly feel like

109
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:57,620
doing something nice for you?

110
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,870
"Suddenly"?

111
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,450
There's gotta be a reason.

112
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:03,920
Mom,

113
00:06:03,980 --> 00:06:05,910
since when does that need a reason?

114
00:06:07,910 --> 00:06:09,080
I take it back,

115
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,370
you have improved.

116
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:13,170
Oh, Mom,

117
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:14,840
I made plans with Chen Jing'an.

118
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,290
We're picnicking tomorrow.

119
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:17,700
There will be an eclipse.

120
00:06:18,370 --> 00:06:19,210
So...

121
00:06:19,450 --> 00:06:20,570
can I

122
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:21,610
skip homework tonight?

123
00:06:23,290 --> 00:06:25,040
Just you and Jing'an?

124
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,490
And Chen Changning,

125
00:06:27,490 --> 00:06:28,910
plus a few others.

126
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,830
Mom, how's the pressure?

127
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:34,210
Not bad.

128
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,000
Mom,

129
00:06:38,910 --> 00:06:39,870
want some tea?

130
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,040
I'll brew you a cup.

131
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:42,540
Enough fussing.

132
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,330
Just say it, how much do you need?

133
00:06:44,650 --> 00:06:47,040
I'm not asking for money.

134
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,830
You're going out. Of course you need money.

135
00:06:50,790 --> 00:06:52,200
But I've improved.

136
00:06:52,580 --> 00:06:54,330
I still have leftover cash
from last time.

137
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,910
Now you've improved.

138
00:06:56,910 --> 00:06:58,080
Obviously.

139
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:00,920
You've spent so much

140
00:07:01,410 --> 00:07:02,620
raising me.

141
00:07:03,410 --> 00:07:04,540
Starting today,

142
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,080
I'll be...

143
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:06,950
frugal.

144
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,660
Thank goodness your dad's not home.

145
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:12,490
If he heard this,

146
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:14,620
he'd just reward you with more money.

147
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:20,160
My good, good boy.

148
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:30,130
Dinner's ready. You're going out?

149
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:34,790
I...

150
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,950
A classmate's birthday.

151
00:07:37,370 --> 00:07:38,210
Everyone's going.

152
00:07:38,740 --> 00:07:40,160
I'd feel bad skipping.

153
00:07:40,490 --> 00:07:41,330
Which classmate?

154
00:07:42,490 --> 00:07:43,330
Deng Shasha.

155
00:07:43,540 --> 00:07:44,380
Deng Shasha?

156
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,330
Is it her birthday today?

157
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,960
Obviously!

158
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,460
Fine, go.

159
00:07:50,490 --> 00:07:51,370
Be back early.

160
00:08:07,490 --> 00:08:08,330
I'm here.

161
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,290
We're picnicking tomorrow,

162
00:08:13,290 --> 00:08:14,490
why meet today?

163
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:16,630
Honestly...

164
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:17,920
I'm nervous.

165
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,290
Are you afraid

166
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:22,740
that I'll steal your spotlight

167
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,200
after switching back?

168
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:25,660
I'd love that.

169
00:08:28,900 --> 00:08:29,790
But...

170
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:30,830
I'm nervous too.

171
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:32,580
Even though I told Niannian

172
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,450
to stay positive earlier...

173
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:36,460
I'm scared.

174
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:38,370
The higher the hopes,
the harder the fall.

175
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:40,290
Chen Jing'an,

176
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,450
no matter what happens,

177
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:44,620
you're the most important to me.

178
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:56,380
What's...

179
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:57,540
this?

180
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,260
Borrowed from the planetarium.

181
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:01,670
Try it?

182
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,200
I don't see anything.

183
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:06,500
Look again.

184
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:10,420
♪Snowflakes blown by the wind♪

185
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:13,990
♪Brush against my hair♪

186
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:16,670
Shh.

187
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:17,900
Look at the stars.

188
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:20,920
♪Covered with the fragrance of time♪

189
00:09:21,210 --> 00:09:24,550
♪That was our youth♪

190
00:09:25,170 --> 00:09:28,050
♪And that boy♪

191
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:34,180
♪Always thought time was long♪

192
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:36,560
♪So many words left unsaid♪

193
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:40,050
♪The path where we held hands♪

194
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:43,670
♪Slowly forgotten♪

195
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:48,160
♪Light passed through petals
and fell on my hand♪

196
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:50,640
♪Shaped into love♪

197
00:09:51,590 --> 00:09:54,150
♪Your burning gaze♪

198
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:56,540
Home yet?

199
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:58,350
(Chen Jing'an)

200
00:09:58,620 --> 00:09:59,460
Yeah.

201
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:04,660
♪Listening to the wind softly sing♪

202
00:10:06,370 --> 00:10:07,580
Don't be late tomorrow.

203
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:11,000
♪Your youthful face♪

204
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,960
Got it.

205
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:15,470
♪Closing my eyes, recalling the past♪

206
00:10:15,470 --> 00:10:18,740
♪The campus, youth, and dreams♪

207
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:21,910
♪And suddenly♪

208
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:26,010
♪Time slips away♪

209
00:10:31,370 --> 00:10:32,370
You're back.

210
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:35,790
Still awake?

211
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,540
Can't sleep.

212
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:41,020
♪Always thought time was long♪

213
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:43,370
♪So many words left unsaid♪

214
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:44,700
Are you worried about

215
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:46,700
you won't switch back?

216
00:10:47,190 --> 00:10:49,750
♪Slowly forgotten♪

217
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,080
Yes, I am.

218
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,580
And also...

219
00:10:54,410 --> 00:10:55,580
that if we do switch back,

220
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:56,420
I'll miss...

221
00:10:58,910 --> 00:10:59,750
miss...

222
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:00,670
your parents.

223
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:04,780
♪Sweetened my summer♪

224
00:11:05,950 --> 00:11:07,120
Let's not overthink it.

225
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:11,910
You'll make it tomorrow.

226
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:14,040
We must succeed.

227
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,450
I've had this bad feeling lately.

228
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,120
Ever since I found out,

229
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,120
more and more people

230
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,160
are learning the truth.

231
00:11:23,370 --> 00:11:24,620
Next, it might be...

232
00:11:25,830 --> 00:11:27,040
our parents.

233
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:29,790
My mom can't know.

234
00:11:29,990 --> 00:11:31,330
She just left the hospital.

235
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:34,160
So even if tomorrow fails,

236
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:36,080
we keep trying.

237
00:11:38,830 --> 00:11:39,790
But I still hope...

238
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:42,240
it works.

239
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:47,160
Got it.

240
00:11:49,490 --> 00:11:50,580
Rest early tonight.

241
00:11:51,330 --> 00:11:52,490
Stay relaxed.

242
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:55,790
Goodnight.

243
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:58,750
Goodnight.

244
00:11:58,750 --> 00:12:03,020
♪Where are you now?♪

245
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:06,690
♪The bell has rung for class's end♪

246
00:12:06,690 --> 00:12:09,750
♪Our story reaches its finale♪

247
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,990
♪Our youth♪

248
00:12:11,990 --> 00:12:17,940
♪Must part ways in the end♪

249
00:12:18,410 --> 00:12:19,660
Jing'an, you're here.

250
00:12:19,830 --> 00:12:20,670
Hello, Ms. Liang.

251
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:21,790
I'm here for Niannian.

252
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:23,040
We're going out later.

253
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:24,380
Come in.

254
00:12:24,410 --> 00:12:26,160
I brought some fruit.

255
00:12:26,450 --> 00:12:27,620
Are you feeling better?

256
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:29,540
Much better. You shouldn't have

257
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:30,830
brought anything.

258
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:31,790
It's heavy, right?

259
00:12:32,490 --> 00:12:34,240
Niannian! Jing'an's here!

260
00:12:34,370 --> 00:12:35,240
Come in.

261
00:12:35,540 --> 00:12:36,380
Have a seat.

262
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:43,930
Aren't we meeting at 10?

263
00:12:43,930 --> 00:12:44,950
Why so early?

264
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:47,200
I wanted to see Mom.

265
00:12:48,410 --> 00:12:50,450
After today, you can see her anytime.

266
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:54,460
Here,

267
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:56,410
Jing'an, have some fruit.

268
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,920
What?

269
00:13:02,620 --> 00:13:04,080
I'm leaving soon.

270
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,240
Just wanted a goodbye hug.

271
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:06,780
Aren't you coming back?

272
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,080
I will.

273
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,740
Oh,

274
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:12,950
I forgot to pack something.

275
00:13:12,990 --> 00:13:13,910
Excuse me.

276
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:16,870
This kid...

277
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:17,990
Jing'an rarely visits,

278
00:13:17,990 --> 00:13:19,290
and you won't even stay?

279
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,410
It's fine, Ms. Liang.

280
00:13:21,410 --> 00:13:22,870
Jing'an, some water?

281
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,960
If you're free,

282
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,990
we could chat.

283
00:13:26,330 --> 00:13:27,170
Of course.

284
00:13:27,290 --> 00:13:29,660
Hey, I heard you switched to liberal arts?

285
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:31,950
Liberal arts means more memorization.

286
00:13:31,950 --> 00:13:32,910
It's tough, you know.

287
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:34,910
It's not too bad.

288
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:37,660
But there are more subjective questions.

289
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:39,160
Sometimes, answering them

290
00:13:39,160 --> 00:13:40,540
really strains my brain.

291
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:41,430
Yeah.

292
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:43,740
Back when Niannian studied liberal arts,

293
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:45,240
she'd always think

294
00:13:45,290 --> 00:13:46,740
her answers were on the right track,

295
